        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>P.J.'s Act</b></p> <p> Amends the Housing and Community Development Act of 1974 to make eligible for community development block grant assistance rehabilitation to improve public safety, including the acquisition, installation, and maintenance of security cameras, safety lighting, and building locking mechanisms in public housing.</p>]]></text>
